---
// /about/ — Phase 5 (2026-05-04). Endorsed Sub-Brand pattern.
// Lead with the parent-brand relationship, then operator credibility, then mission.
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About &mdash; A service of Agni Consulting | Agni AI Store"
  description="Agni AI Store is the customer-lifecycle service of Agni Consulting, a B2B marketing-ops practice based in Toronto and serving North America. Built by operators who&rsquo;ve shipped this stack inside Series-A and Series-B SaaS, brought down to where it&rsquo;s genuinely needed."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="ai-hero">
    <p class="ai-eyebrow">ABOUT</p>
    <h1>By operators, <br>not an agency.</h1>
    <p class="ai-lead">
      Agni AI Store is the customer-lifecycle service of <a href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);">Agni Consulting</a> &mdash; a B2B marketing-operations practice based in Toronto and serving North America. We took the playbook that runs inside venture-backed B2B SaaS companies and rebuilt it for owner-operated service businesses.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Operator -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">The operator</p>
      <h2>Aman Gupta.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:18px;">
        I&rsquo;m Aman. I run <a href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);">Agni Consulting</a> &mdash; a marketing-ops practice that&rsquo;s spent the last decade inside Series-A and Series-B B2B SaaS companies wiring HubSpot, Marketo, Salesforce, RevOps, and demand generation. The unsexy plumbing that decides whether a company hits its number.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        Agni AI Store is the version of that work I built for local service businesses. The shape of the problem is identical &mdash; someone is leaking customers, the leak is operational, the owner doesn&rsquo;t have time to fix it &mdash; but the vocabulary, the software, the regulations, and the dollar amounts are different. We use industry-specific terms (recall, reactivation, care plan, agreement attach) because those are the words that match how owner-operators actually run their businesses.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        I started this division after watching a friend who runs an independent vet clinic lose six figures a year to voicemail and lapsed clients &mdash; and realising the playbook I run for SaaS companies would solve almost all of it, with a fraction of the technical lift. The first conversations were free. They still are. The audit is the offer.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The relationship -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">Parent brand</p>
      <h2>How Agni AI Store relates to Agni Consulting.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:16px;">
        <a href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);">Agni Consulting</a> is the parent practice. It serves B2B SaaS companies $5M&ndash;$50M ARR with on-demand marketing leadership &mdash; fractional CMO, demand-gen overhauls, marketing-ops audits, RevOps integration. Different audience, same operator, same operational discipline.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        Agni AI Store is the productized service-business arm. We take the same operational backbone &mdash; lifecycle ops, automation, AI agents, integration plumbing &mdash; and apply it to vet clinics, chiropractors, dental practices, med-spas, HVAC operators, and the dozens of other owner-operated service businesses that have the same four leaks.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:14px;">
        Two domains, two distinct ICPs, one team, one quality bar. If you&rsquo;re looking for fractional CMO or B2B SaaS marketing-ops work, that&rsquo;s on the <a href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);">Agni Consulting</a> site. If you&rsquo;re an owner-operator running a service business, you&rsquo;re in the right place here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Geography -->
  <section class="ai-section-tight">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow">
      <p class="ai-eyebrow">Where we work</p>
      <h2>North America today. Globally over time.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--tx-soft);line-height:1.75;margin-top:16px;">
        Our team is based in Toronto. We serve clients across Canada and the United States, with engagements in Europe by referral. We invoice in USD by default; Canadian clients can opt into CAD. Twilio numbers are local to your area code regardless of where you are. Data residency, HIPAA BAAs, and PIPEDA-aware practices are configured per-engagement &mdash; details on the <a href="/trust/" style="color:var(--accent);">trust page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ai-section">
    <div class="ai-wrap ai-narrow" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>Talk to the operator who&rsquo;ll run your account.</h2>
      <p class="ai-lead">No SDR, no junior. The 30-minute audit is with me. The implementation team is small, senior, and the same people month after month.</p>
      <div class="ai-cta-row">
        <a class="ai-btn" href="https://calendly.com/aman-shopagni" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book the audit &rarr;</a>
        <a class="ai-btn-ghost" href="https://shopagni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Agni Consulting</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
